    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.43 * wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.35)))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = 0.23
    v2 = 0.11
    v1 = v2
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.42 / tmp + 0.45)) * ((tmp + 0.42 * v1 + 0.39) + (v1 + 0.40 * v0 + 0.63)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.47 * v0 + 0.91)))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
